definitions.definition: Of a person : slightly overweight , somewhat fat , and hence plump , rounded , and soft .
examples: Obviously the chubby child was eating too much.

definitions.definition: Of a body part : containing a moderate amount of fat.
examples: It’s quite normal for babies to have chubby cheeks.
